&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Reunion Marketing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reunion Marketing is a dynamic and forward-thinking agency specializing in digital marketing for the Automotive industry. We drive success through data-driven strategies and innovative campaign management. Join our team of passionate professionals committed to delivering measurable results for our Automotive Clients.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a traditional SEO role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a highly capable &lt;strong&gt;Senior SEO &amp;amp; Content Strategist&lt;/strong&gt; who thrives at the intersection of SEO, AI-assisted content production, technical execution, and operational ownership. This is a hands-on role for someone who doesn’t just create strategy decks—they execute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll own organic search execution across a portfolio of clients, taking projects from idea to publish with minimal oversight. One hour you may be diagnosing ranking declines, the next you’re refining AI-generated content, building pages in a CMS, writing schema markup, or optimizing production workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy autonomy, solving problems quickly, and building efficient systems in fast-moving environments, you’ll fit right in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own SEO Execution from Start to Finish&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll manage and execute organic search initiatives across multiple client accounts—balancing strategy, production, technical SEO, and delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead AI-Assisted Content Production&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and refine SEO-driven content using tools like ChatGPT, Gemini, and Jasper&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build scalable workflows that improve production speed without compromising quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate AI output critically for accuracy, SEO value, and brand alignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce location pages, service pages, blogs, and ad hoc SEO projects at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build &amp;amp; Publish Pages Yourself&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly inside CMS platforms to build and launch pages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use HTML and CSS to improve structure, readability, UX, and layout quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement metadata, internal linking, schema, and on-page SEO best practices during production—not after the fact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Operational Excellence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own SEO production scheduling and workflow coordination&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor errors, identify bottlenecks, and proactively solve issues before they impact performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep projects moving in a high-volume, deadline-driven environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate Across Teams&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with SEO leadership, paid media, social, and operations teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Step in as backup support for SEO leadership when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help align organic initiatives with broader marketing and client growth strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’re someone who can think strategically while still enjoying the execution side of the work. You’re resourceful, highly organized, and comfortable owning outcomes independently.&lt;/p&gt;
